text: Tønsberg is a city and municipality in Vestfold county, Norway. In 2022, 57,794 people live in Tønsberg. Wildlife: The Osmoderma eremita is a beetle; The only municipality in Norway that has it, is Tønsberg (as of 2024).https://www.nrk.no/vestfoldogtelemark/fikk-besok-av-den-sjeldne- eremittbillen_-_-et-mysterium-1.16971356.
